ium innovation success stories airware® automotive body sheet specifications product portfolio innovations for crash management systems our technology center and services our technology networks and best practice councils partnerships innovation at constellium aluminium is more than a metal it is the material that takes the shape of our ideas  so that our ideas may shape the world sustainability life cycle of aluminium our role in the lifecycle of aluminium three essentials on aluminium recycling case studies  automotive parts and beverage cans people health and safety motivation and engagement skill development gender diversity community engagement our approach to aluminium recycling objectives and targets operations energy efficiency climate change preventing pollution reducing waste responsible business external recognitions materiality assessment managing sustainability ethical business practices engaging our suppliers in sustainability conflict minerals products customer satisfaction innovation ecodesign material safety data sheets constellium is committed to preserving our natural resources and wholeheartedly promotes aluminium recycling as part of our industrial strategies print home  sustainability life cycle of aluminium our approach to aluminium recycling objectives and targets responsible business products people operations our sustainability charter we are committed to developing producing and selling sustainable products that meet our customer needs now and in the futurewe will  maximize recycling rates of our products including after end of use life  continuously innovate and offer lighter safer and infinitely recyclable solutions we are committed to ensuring our people are safe skilled motivated and engagedwe will  protect the safety and health of our employees contractors and visitors as a top priority  strive to enhance employee engagement and development we are committed to minimizing the environmental impact of all our operations in terms of energy waste and waterwe will  further develop recycling  optimize the use of natural resources especially energy  prevent and minimize environmental impacts we are committed to undertaking the highest standards of governance of our activities in line with the constellium’s valueswe will  subscribe to the highest levels of transparency and accountability and commit to develop company and industry sustainability programs  promote the adoption and implementation of sustainability policies by our suppliers and contractors business and sustainability performance report  quick links  constellium at a glance  where we are  news and press releases  multimedia library  work with us constellium websites  constellium soft alloys europe  constellium hard and soft alloys czech republic  constellium ravenswood plants sellsite  ctec services  legal notice  rss feeds  site map  contact  constellium  quality aluminum semiproducts manufacturing company  constellium constellium uses cookies in order to analyze the frequentation rate of its website or interactions with social networks by pursuing your navigation you accept the use of these cookies for further information about the use of cookies or the opposition proceedings click here   constellium websites  contact us follow us media news and press releases multimedia library literature   news  media access constellium news press releases pictures videos publications and presentations candidates discover our jobs production and processes research and development lean experts environment health and safety sales and marketing support functions work with us why join constellium constellium job offers how to join constellium constellium university meet us students and apprentices graduates experts   careers join constellium to take full advantage of the opportunities that aluminium presents investors financial results and presentation earnings results annual and interim reports investor presentations analyst day regulatory filings stock pric