ars constellium nv is headquartered in rue washington france aluminum innovation research  development lab  technology networks  constellium websites  contact us follow us media news and press releases multimedia library literature   news  media access constellium news press releases pictures videos publications and presentations candidates discover our jobs production and processes research and development lean experts environment health and safety sales and marketing support functions work with us why join constellium constellium job offers how to join constellium constellium university meet us students and apprentices graduates experts   careers join constellium to take full advantage of the opportunities that aluminium presents investors financial results and presentation earnings results annual and interim reports investor presentations analyst day regulatory filings stock price cstm investors contact     about constellium who we are industrial platform our locations děčín czech republic issoire france muscle shoals usa neufbrisach france ravenswood usa singen germany valais switzerland corporate governance board of directors executive committee annual general meetings about aluminium glossary finance financial results and presentation regulatory filings stock price cstm investors contact what we do environment health and safety ehs about constellium a global leader in aluminium transformation constellium designs and manufactures innovative and high valueadded aluminium products and components business  solutions aerospace and transportation products services brands markets research and innovation standards and certifications manufacturing sites packaging and automotive rolled products sheets and coils functional surfaces innovation in sheets  coils sustainability manufacturing sites automotive structures and industry automotive system solutions automotive technology and services automotive structures manufacturing sites extrusions products technologies and ser