tributes and commitments that set us apart from the competitionour vision and valuesas a team and with the support of all our stakeholders we want constellium to become the most profitable company in our industry to achieve this goal we will rely on  team work and mutual trust  entrepreneurship and decisiveness  sense of urgency and decentralized decision making  responsibility and accountability  rigor and discipline  transparency and highest standards of ethics   we will strive relentlessly for value creation through growth operational improvement and innovation in all aspects of our businesswe will respect develop and protect our people serve our customers and write our future togetherour attributes  technical challenges innovate and create solutions that meet the rigorous specifications of our clients working at the forefront of major industries including aerospace automotive and packaging  innovative materials push the boundaries and capabilities of aluminium a recyclable material with almost endless applications    safe operating environment gain reassurance working with a company where safety is anchored in our culture and always at the forefront of our thinking  history and culture be motivated as part of a new company that traces its history to the beginning of aluminium production and which has built on a lean culture of safety bestinclass customer portfolio commercial and operational excellence innovation and talent  human values join a global team where employees are visible talent is nurtured and respect is universal  career opportunities develop your career with mobility opportunities that range from product and process development to rd ehs lean transformation sales etc our commitments  delivering excellence constellium’s workforce shares the common ambition to deliver value and efficiency in all its activities this is one of the reasons that we count among our customers some of the world’s largest and most respected companies  creative collaboration constellium works with customers to forge strong integrated partnerships and transform creative concepts into highquality actionable solutions  advancing innovation constellium sets the industry standard generating value by virtue of our expertise and innovation  excellence in ehs constellium’s respect for people and the environment in which we live governs our priorities and drives our reputation as a company  discover our jobs  meet us quick links  constellium at a glance  where we are  news and press releases  multimedia library  work with us constellium websites  constellium soft alloys europe  constellium hard and soft alloys czech republic  constellium ravenswood plants sellsite  ctec services  legal notice  rss feeds  site map  contact  constellium  finance  aluminium supplier  constellium websites  contact us follow us media news and press releases multimedia library literature   news  media access constellium news press releases pictures videos publications and presentations candidates discover our jobs production and processes research and development lean experts environment health and safety sales and marketing support functions work with us why join constellium constellium job offers how to join constellium constellium university meet us students and apprentices graduates experts   careers join constellium to take full advantage of the opportunities that aluminium presents investors financial results and presentation earnings results annual and interim reports investor presentations analyst day regulatory filings stock price cstm investors contact     about constellium who we are industrial platform our locations děčín czech republic issoire france muscle shoals usa neufbrisach france ravenswood usa singen germany valais switzerland corporate governance board of directors executive committee annual general meetings about aluminium glossary finance financial results and presentation regulatory filings stock price cstm investors contact what we do environ