usiness units  aerospace and transportation  packaging and automotive rolled products  automotive structures and industry products  rolled products plates sheets and coils  extrusions customized profiles large profiles soft and hard alloy profiles tubes and bars  automotive structures crash management systems other safety systems cockpit carriers bodyinwhite structural components  over  active patent families positioning   worldwide for aerospace plates   worldwide in closure stock   in north america for wide coils   in europe for large profiles   in europe for hard alloy extrusions   worldwide in crash management systems cms   shared in europe in autobody sheet   in europe for can body stock   in north america for can body stock subscribe to newsletter finance get relevant news and all financial information by signing up to our irmailing list email    privacy investors contacts ryan wentling phone number    click here to send an email latest earnings results news monday  july  constellium to report second quarter  results on july   tuesday  june  constellium to showcase its aluminium bright surfaces and its d app at the  automotive inter monday  june  constellium releases annual business and sustainability report reflecting progress towards  s friday  june  voting results from constelliums  annual general meeting tuesday  june  constellium to present new aerospace innovations at paris air show all news spotlight download the business and sustainability performance report  last update  april  quick links  constellium at a glance  where we are  news and press releases  multimedia library  work with us constellium websites  constellium soft alloys europe  constellium hard and soft alloys czech republic  constellium ravenswood plants sellsite  ctec services  legal notice  rss feeds  site map  contact  constellium